Package: ForestSDC
Type: Package
Title: Forest stand Structure, tree Diversity, and species Composition
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ernesto Rubio
Maintainer: Ernesto Rubio <ernestorub@gmail.com>
Description: The package provides tools for forest inventory analysis, including functions to calculate structural diversity indices, biodiversity metrics, and Nearest Neighbour Summary Statistics. It is designed to support 
    researchers and practitioners in assessing forest dynamics, ecosystem health, and biodiversity.
